text: Lunania is a genus of flowering plants in the willow family, Salicaceae. ==Selected species== * Lunania cubensis Turczaninov * Lunania dodecandra Wright * Lunania elongata Britton & P.Wilson * Lunania polydactyla Urban * Lunania racemosa Hook. ==References== Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Salicaceae genera
title: Lunania
